{
  "stem": "22959.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I went back to Zdzieciol after the war, and I did not expect to find much, but I found much less than I expected.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Zdzieciol looked like a little village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I remember that I used-- I liked to skate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had a river in our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In wintertime, it was frozen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went skating on the river, and ice broke, and I fell into the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one boy was going to rescue me, so he walked on the ice, and he also fell in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then they took us out, and I remember they took us to a neighborhood house, and they gave us some vodka to drink so nothing would happen to us because everything was frozen, everything what we had on was frozen.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And nothing happened to us, but it was quite an experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I was at the time, I think about 12, 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came to school, and I told the story to my teacher, and I told him that I fell into the water, and he called me, in Polish, [POLISH], that means that I fell in the water.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the water-- wintertime, can you imagine, I mean, it's so cold-- I was in the water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is also something to remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm glad you asked me, and I could tell you about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] You don't remember that it ever existed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was so long, long, long time ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My memory is that it was a beautiful town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle lived in Vilna, as I mentioned before, so when I came to Vilna, I lived with them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I attended the Real-Gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
